  "short_text": "Second Character in the Word",
  "content": "For this problem, the prefilled code will contain a function. Write a program that the given function will return the second character in the word passed to the function.<hr><b>Input</b><br/><br/>The first line of input will contain a string.<hr><b>Output</b><br/><br/>The output should be a single line containing the second character of the given word.<hr><b>Explanation</b><br/><br/>For example, if the given word is &quot;MATHS&quot;, your code should print the second character in the given word, which is &quot;A&quot;.",
